                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny morning. Slight chance of a shower, most likely in the evening. Winds northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to around 6 with daytime temperatures reaching around 16.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-06-29T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-30T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-28T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-29T14:30:00Z">
